# Master secret — root of trust for this Mnemion instance.
#
# The "Deploy to Cloudflare" button reads this file and prompts for each value,
# storing them as encrypted Worker secrets (never committed).
#
# Generate a high-entropy value, e.g.:  openssl rand -hex 32
#
# If you leave it empty, the instance comes up in INSECURE dev mode (auth is
# auto-approved). Set it for any real deployment. After deploying, register your
# owner passkey once at:  https://<your-worker>.workers.dev/setup?token=<secret>
MNEMION_SECRET=
